features: 【2X VALUE for 1/2 COST】Looking to stock up on notebooks for employees, events, or personal use? Tired of repeatedly buying expensive notebooks? Our bulk-packaged notebooks offer a COST-EFFECTIVE solution! It can be used as a writing journal, daily journal, business notebook, note taking journal, and more. The superior craftsmanship and individual packaging also make it a PERFECT GIFT for friends!

【Thick Pages for Writing Without Limits】Large A5 size (5.75"x 8.38"/146mm x 213mm), 27 lines per page with 7mm spacing, total 320 pages, include 312 NUMBERED PAGES/156 sheets to provide you ample space to write. Our INNOVATIVE PAPER TECHNOLOGY on 100GSM thick paper ensures a perfect canvas for your ideas - no bleed, no ghosting.

【User-Centered Design】5 Contents Pages for logging more entries; 2 Ribbon bookmarks for quick content reference; 1 Elastic closure band for secure page keeping; 1 Pen holder to keep your pen always handy; 1 Back Inner pocket for storing notes and small items; 8 Sheets of perforated page for versatile use.

【Tough & Stylish Hardcover】Crafted from TOP-NOTCH VEGAN LEATHER with distinctive patterns, which is animal-friendly and boasts a luxurious look. DURABLE hard cover provides superior protection to your pages compared to softcover, while offering a stable writing surface. Featuring an innovative thread-bound binding that allows for easy LAY-FLAT use, catering to both left- and right-handed users.

【FREE Index Tabs Stickers】Each leather bound journal comes with 1 gift of multicolor index tabs stickers for papers classifying and marking. The free index stickers also can help you mark and identify your subjects, you can quickly flip to the section you're looking for.

Page count, lines per page, and line spacing? Each notebook has total 320 pages (equal to 160 sheets, 1 sheet = 2 pages), incl. personal info page + 5 index pages + 312 numbered pages. A5: 27 lines each page. Standard College Ruled, 7mm line spacing. Why are there page numbers and 5 index pages? 1.Easy navigation: Page numbers & index pages for quick access to notes & sections. 2.Better organization: Categorize & archive notes by topic or date. 3.Efficient reference: Index pages provide a visual overview, saving time in finding information. Is the paper thick enough? Will it bleed through? We have employed exclusive innovative paper technology on our 100gsm thick paper to provide a perfect canvas for your ideas - no bleeding, no ghosting. We have tested writing with various popular pen brands and confirmed no ink penetration. What binding method is used? Is it lay-flat and lefty-friendly? We use innovative thread binding, allowing the notebook to lay flat at 180°, accommodating left-handed and right-handed users. This binding method ensures durability and prevents loose or detached pages, surpassing glue binding in reliability. What are the colors included in each of the two mixed sets? The colors included in the bright mixed set are: Pink, Black, Teal, Yellow, and Burgundy. The colors included in the dark mixed set are: Blue, Grey Blue, Black, Green, and Brown.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well Made and Beautiful
reviews.reviewText: These exceeded my expectations. They seem well-made, and the burgundy color is perfect. The cover is definitely hard, not flimsy like many others, the paper is smooth, the lines are clear without being too dark, the pages are numbered, comes with tabs, a back pocket, and an unnumbered table of contents in order to find text easier, a pen holder, and even a color-coordinated elastic band to hold the book closed in a purse or book bag. They are a perfect size for travel and don't take up much room on a desk or bedside table.They are so beautiful that I'm feeling a bit hesitant about writing in them as what goes into them has to be as beautiful and as valuable as they look. Looks like I will have to just buy another set or two... Off I go to order another one. Love them.They are at a decent sale price currently. I'm not sure I would pay more than the current reduced price of $30. As long as they are this price or less, they will have a regular buyer for life.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I really love these!:) They are a perfect size, and a quality product. They are everything all the positive reviews say. They come individually wrapped - something I really appreciate!:) - in a little box of their own. I love the bookmarks, the pen holder, the closure band holder, and the little pocket in back. The pages are numbered, and there is a table of contents in the front. The college lined pages are also what I wanted. They even come with some free stickers!:) I do wish they came in more colors. Pastels and brighter colors would be nice, and more energizing than the darker colors. I got the dark green, though, and really like it.:) The price point for the quality you get is fantastic!:)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The (almost) perfect journal
reviews.reviewText: I've been journaling almost daily for the last 10 years. Needless to say, I've gone through a lot of journals and notebooks over the years. These journals are great quality at a fair price. The pages are nice and thick and my ink doesn't smear. I like the sticky bookmarks that are included, and the ribbon marker that is built into the design of the journal. My only complaint is minor, and that is, I wish it was slightly larger. It would be more comfortable to write in, especially as you near the bottom of the page. Otherwise, these are the best journals I have found yet.
